/\n40:   - Purpose: Set binary output directory\n41:   - File: `Makefile`\n42:   - Verification: `grep \"BINDIR ?= bin/\" Makefile`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T1.6**: Define GO_VERSION, GOLANGCI_LINT_VERSION, CONTROLLER_TOOLS_VERSION variables\n45:   - Purpose: Pin tool versions for CI alignment\n46:   - File: `Makefile`\n47:   - Verification: `grep \"GO_VERSION ?= 1.24\" Makefile && grep \"GOLANGCI_LINT_VERSION\" Makefile`\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T1.7**: Define LOCALBIN and tool paths (CONTROLLER_GEN, GOLANGCI_LINT)\n50:   - Purpose: Local tool installation paths\n51:   - File: `Makefile`\n52:   - Verification: `grep \"LOCALBIN ?= $(shell pwd)/bin\" Makefile`\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T1.8**: Define E2E cluster variables (E2E_CLUSTER_NAME, AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION)\n55:   - Purpose: E2E test environment configuration\n56:   - File: `Makefile`\n57:   - Verification: `grep \"E2E_CLUSTER_NAME ?= agentcube-e2e\" Makefile`\n58: \n59: - [ ] **T1.9**: Set SHELL to bash with pipefail\n60:   - Purpose: Ensure reliable shell execution\n61:   - File: `Makefile`\n62:   - Verification: `grep \"SHELL ?= /usr/bin/env bash -o pipefail\" Makefile`\n63: \n64: ### Phase 2: Build Targets (ST-2)\n65: \n66: - [ ] **T2.1**: Add .PHONY declaration for all build targets\n67:   - Purpose: Mark targets as phony (not file-based)\n68:   - File: `Makefile`\n69:   - Verification: `grep \".PHONY: all build build-\" Makefile`\n70: \n71: - [ ] **T2.2**: Create all target with dependency on build\n72:   - Purpose: Default target for complete build\n73:   - File: `Makefile`\n74:   - Verification: `grep \"^all: build\" Makefile`\n75: \n76: - [ ] **T2.3**: Create build target with ## documentation comment\n77:   - Purpose: Build all 7 binaries with single target\n78:   - File: `Makefile`\n79:   - Verification: `grep \"^build:.*## Build all binaries\" Makefile`\n80: \n81: - [ ] **T2.4**: Add go build for workloadmanager binary\n82:   - Purpose: Build workload-manager component\n83:   - File: `Makefile`\n84:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/workloadmanager ./cmd/workload-manager\" Makefile`\n85: \n86: - [ ] **T2.5**: Add go build for router binary\n87:   - Purpose: Build router component\n88:   - File: `Makefile`\n89:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/router ./cmd/router\" Makefile`\n90: \n91: - [ ] **T2.6**: Add go build for picod binary\n92:   - Purpose: Build picod component\n93:   - File: `Makefile`\n94:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/picod ./cmd/picod\" Makefile`\n95: \n96: - [ ] **T2.7**: Add go build for agentd binary\n97:   - Purpose: Build agent daemon component\n98:   - File: `Makefile`\n99:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/agentd ./cmd/agentd\" Makefile`\n100: \n101: - [ ] **T2.8**: Add go build for agentctl binary\n102:   - Purpose: Build agent CLI tool\n103:   - File: `Makefile`\n104:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/agentctl ./cmd/agentctl\" Makefile`\n105: \n106: - [ ] **T2.9**: Add go build for agentcube binary\n107:   - Purpose: Build agentcube CLI\n108:   - File: `Makefile`\n109:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/agentcube ./cmd/agentcube\" Makefile`\n110: \n111: - [ ] **T2.10**: Add go build for agentsandbox binary\n112:   - Purpose: Build sandbox binary\n113:   - File: `Makefile`\n114:   - Verification: `grep \"go build -o bin/agentsandbox ./cmd/agentsandbox\" Makefile`\n115: \n116: ### Phase 3: Individual Binary Targets (ST-3)\n117: \n118: - [ ] **T3.1**: Create build-workloadmanager target with generate dependency\n119:   - Purpose: Build workloadmanager binary only\n120:   - File: `Makefile`\n121:   - Verification: `grep \"^build-workloadmanager: generate.*##\" Makefile`\n122: \n123: - [ ] **T3.2**: Create build-router target with generate dependency\n124:   - Purpose: Build router binary only\n125:   - File: `Makefile`\n126:   - Verification: `grep \"^build-router: generate.*##\" Makefile`\n127: \n128: - [ ] **T3.3**: Create build-picod target with generate dependency\n129:   - Purpose: Build picod binary only\