kefile && grep \"GOOS=darwin GOARCH=amd64\" Makefile`\n174: \n175: - [ ] **T4.4**: Create build-darwin-arm64 target with GOOS/GOARCH\n176:   - Purpose: Build for Darwin ARM64\n177:   - File: `Makefile`\n178:   - Verification: `grep \"^build-darwin-arm64:\" Makefile && grep \"GOOS=darwin GOARCH=arm64\" Makefile`\n179: \n180: ### Phase 5: Test Targets (ST-5)\n181: \n182: - [ ] **T5.1**: Add .PHONY declaration for test targets\n183:   - Purpose: Mark test targets as phony\n184:   - File: `Makefile`\n185:   - Verification: `grep \".PHONY:.*test\" Makefile`\n186: \n187: - [ ] **T5.2**: Create test target with ## documentation\n188:   - Purpose: Run unit tests with verbose output\n189:   - File: `Makefile`\n190:   - Verification: `grep \"^test:.*## Run unit tests\" Makefile`\n191: \n192: - [ ] **T5.3**: Add go test -v ./... command\n193:   - Purpose: Execute Go tests\n194:   - File: `Makefile`\n195:   - Verification: `grep \"go test -v ./...\" Makefile`\n196: \n197: - [ ] **T5.4**: Create test-coverage target with ## documentation\n198:   - Purpose: Generate coverage report\n199:   - File: `Makefile`\n200:   - Verification: `grep \"^test-coverage:.*##\" Makefile`\n201: \n202: - [ ] **T5.5**: Add coverage.out generation with -coverprofile\n203:   - Purpose: Generate coverage data file\n204:   - File: `Makefile`\n205:   - Verification: `grep \"go test -coverprofile=coverage.out\" Makefile`\n206: \n207: - [ ] **T5.6**: Add coverage.html generation with go tool cover\n208:   - Purpose: Generate HTML coverage report\n209:   - File: `Makefile`\n210:   - Verification: `grep \"go tool cover -html=coverage.out\" Makefile`\n211: \n212: - [ ] **T5.7**: Create test-race target with ## documentation\n213:   - Purpose: Run tests with race detector\n214:   - File: `Makefile`\n215:   - Verification: `grep \"^test-race:.*##\" Makefile`\n216: \n217: - [ ] **T5.8**: Add go test -race ./... command\n218:   - Purpose: Execute race condition detection\n219:   - File: `Makefile`\n220:   - Verif