efile` |\n925: | Phase 7 | `grep \"^generate:.*##\" Makefile && grep \"controller-gen\" Makefile` |\n926: | Phase 8 | `grep \"^docker-build:.*##\" Makefile` |\n927: | Phase 9 | `grep \"docker buildx build\" Makefile && grep \"linux/amd64,linux/arm64\" Makefile` |\n928: | Phase 10 | `grep \"kind load docker-image\" Makefile` |\n929: | Phase 11 | `grep \"^e2e:.*##\" Makefile && grep \"./test/e2e/run_e2e.sh\" Makefile` |\n930: | Phase 12 | `grep \"^install:.*##\" Makefile && grep \"INSTALL_PREFIX\" Makefile` |\n931: | Phase 13 | `grep \"^clean:.*##\" Makefile && grep \"rm -rf bin/\" Makefile` |\n932: | Phase 14 | `grep \"^help:.*##\" Makefile && grep \"awk.*##\" Makefile` |\n933: | Phase 15 | `make --dry-run help 2>/dev/null` |\n934: | Phase 16 | `make build && ls bin/workloadmanager` |\n935: | Phase 17 | `make test-coverage && test -f coverage.out` |\n936: | Phase 18 | `make lint` |\n937: | Phase 19 | `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test` |\n938: | Phase 20 | `make clean && test ! -d bin/` |\n939: | Phase 21 | `make help | grep \"Build\"` |\n940: | Phase 22 | `make build VERSION=test-override BINDIR=test-bin` |\n941: \n942: ---\n943: \n944: ## Acceptance Criteria\n945: \n946: - [ ] Makefile has all 9 variable definitions (IMAGE_REPO, VERSION, TARGETOS, TARGETARCH, BINDIR, GO_VERSION, GOLANGCI_LINT_VERSION, CONTROLLER_TOOLS_VERSION, INSTALL_PREFIX)\n947: - [ ] Makefile has all 7 binary build targets (workloadmanager, router, picod, agentd, agentctl, agentcube, agentsandbox)\n948: - [ ] Makefile has 4 cross-compile targets (linux-amd64, linux-arm64, darwin-amd64, darwin-arm64)\n949: - [ ] Makefile has test, test-coverage, test-race targets\n950: - [ ] Makefile has fmt, vet, lint, gen-check, gen-copyright targets\n951: - [ ] Makefile has generate, gen-crd, gen-client, gen-all targets\n952: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build, docker-build-router, docker-build-picod, docker-build-all targets\n953: - [ ] Makefile has docker-buildx-push, docker-buildx-push-router