install $(2)@$(3) ; }\n1002: endef\n1003: ```\n1004: \n1005: ### Binary Build Pattern\n1006: \n1007: ```makefile\n1008: build-workloadmanager: generate ## Build workloadmanager binary only\n1009: \tgo build -o bin/workloadmanager ./cmd/workload-manager\n1010: ```\n1011: \n1012: ### Docker Build Pattern\n1013: \n1014: ```makefile\n1015: docker-build: ## Build workloadmanager Docker image\n1016: \tdocker build \\\n1017: \t\t-f docker/Dockerfile \\\n1018: \t\t-t $(IMAGE_REPO)/workloadmanager:$(VERSION) \\\n1019: \t\t--build-arg TARGETOS=$(TARGETOS) \\\n1020: \t\t--build-arg TARGETARCH=$(TARGETARCH) \\\n1021: \t\t.\n1022: ```\n1023: \n1024: ### Cross-Compile Pattern\n1025: \n1026: ```makefile\n1027: build-linux-amd64: generate ## Build for Linux AMD64\n1028: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -o bin/workloadmanager ./cmd/workload-manager\n1029: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -o bin/router ./cmd/router\n1030: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -o bin/picod ./cmd/picod\n1031: ```\n1032: \n1033: ---\n1034: \n1035: ## Implementation Timeline\n1036: \n1037: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n1038: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n1039: | Phase 1: Variable System | T1.1-T1.9 | Pending | 0% |\n1040: | Phase 2: Build Targets | T2.1-T2.10 | Pending | 0% |\n1041: | Phase 3: Individual Binary Targets | T3.1-T3.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1042: | Phase 4: Cross-Compile Targets | T4.1-T4.4 | Pending | 0% |\n1043: | Phase 5: Test Targets | T5.1-T5.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1044: | Phase 6: Quality Targets | T6.1-T6.13 | Pending | 0% |\n1045: | Phase 7: Codegen Targets | T7.1-T7.9 | Pending | 0% |\n1046: | Phase 8: Docker Build Targets | T8.1-T8.10 | Pending | 0% |\n1047: | Phase 9: Docker Multi-Arch | T9.1-T9.9 | Pending | 0% |\n1048: | Phase 10: Kind Load Targets | T10.1-T10.6 | Pending | 0% |\n1049: | Phase 11: E2E Targets | T11.1-T11.8 | Pending | 0% |\n1050: | Phase 12: Install Targets | T12.1-T12.12 | Pending | 0% |\n1051: | Phase 13: Clean Targets | T13.1-T13.7 | Pending | 